            <div type="translation">
                <p>Hail, Mary, full of grace. The Lord is with you.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is based on the dialogue between the Archangel Gabriel and the Virgin according to Luke 1:28, 38. The addition of the name of the Virgin after Χαῖρε κεχαριτωμένη, which is absent in the evangelical text, appears also in the inscription of Sotera. </p>
            </div>
